ctory/Repository Layout\\\\n- All files in single directory.\\\\n- Data file (`todo.json`) ignored from source control.\\\\n\\\\n---\\\\nThis design enables rapid development, simplicity, and future feature additions while maintaining clear separation of concerns.\\\"}\",\"name\":\"board_write_file\"}],\"type\":\"ToolCallRequestEvent\"},{\"id\":\"b8ab3f10-c4a3-427e-b9a1-c880ea2c2da1\",\"source\":\"Architect\",\"models_usage\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"created_at\":\"2026-03-16T07:24:57.623706Z\",\"content\":[{\"content\":\"Successfully wrote to data/project_board/todo_cli_json/ARCHITECTURE.md\",\"name\":\"board_write_file\",\"call_id\":\"call_KRV472T6F6sIzkGhq5CTr0pI\",\"is_error\":false}],\"type\":\"ToolCallExecutionEvent\"}]},\"name\":\"Architect\"}", "sender": "Architect_eb26f318-3432-47b4-9380-ff7a11d5fd63/eb26f318-3432-47b4-9380-ff7a11d5fd63", "receiver": null, "kind": "MessageKind.PUBLISH", "delivery_stage": "DeliveryStage.DELIVER", "type": "Message"}
