\n- Simple, flat JSON structure; adequate for personal/small-scale use\\n- Easy to refactor for more complex features later\\n\\n## Directory/Repository Layout\\n- All files in single directory.\\n- Data file (`todo.json`) ignored from source control.\\n\\n---\\nThis design enables rapid development, simplicity, and future feature additions while maintaining clear separation of concerns.\",\"name\":\"board_read_file\",\"call_id\":\"call_TtlEYSvLGAnMIVTblkq6ixiX\",\"is_error\":false}],\"type\":\"ToolCallExecutionEvent\"}]},\"name\":\"ProjectManager\"}", "sender": "ProjectManager_eb26f318-3432-47b4-9380-ff7a11d5fd63/eb26f318-3432-47b4-9380-ff7a11d5fd63", "receiver": null, "kind": "MessageKind.PUBLISH", "delivery_stage": "DeliveryStage.DELIVER", "type": "Message"}
